lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Bernard Tomic was knocked out of the Istanbul Open, losing to unseeded Diego Schwartzman of Argentina 6-2, 6-2 on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Top-Seeded Bernard Tomic Knocked Out of Istanbul Open
